Revolutionary Urban Design
Dark Sky City Concept

Mandatory lights-out: All non-essential lighting shuts off at sunset
Automated shuttering: Businesses operate with light-blocking window covers
Underground nightlife: Entertainment and commerce continue below ground
Wildlife protection: Natural night environment preserved for fauna

